uct adaptations\nCustomised product developments\nPerfect product implementation\nRealising smooth process flows\nStock and logistics concepts\nFind out more!\n/ ASHCROFT EPC\nIT’S YOUR PROJECT AND WE UNDERSTAND YOUR CHALLENGES. WE LIVE AND UNDERSTAND THE EPC PROJECT BUSINESS AND HAVE DONE SO FOR OVER 160 YEARS.\nNo pressure and temperature measurement manufacturer has our global project history.\nGlobal presence and local support\nPlanning / Design\nDocumentations\nOn-site inspections\nPerfect logistics\nAfter Sales Support\nFind out more!\n/ THIS IS ASHCROFT\nHISTORY, PRESENCE &amp; TRADITION\nDevelopment out of tradition\nTimes have changed, but not our attitude.\nMore\nOur core values\nOur corporate values are not abstract, but are lived by us.\nMore\n/ CERTIFIED QUALITY\nTHE USE OF PRODUCTS IN SAFETY-CRITICAL APPLICATIONS REQUIRES APPROVALS AND TESTS AT THE HIGHEST LEVEL.\nThat is why we have established a quality assurance system according to ISO 9001 in all plants, which is supplemented by further systems for ATEX or ISO 17025.As our products are used in complex safety-critical applications, we also certify them for functional safety SIL.The materials used are traceably sourced from reliable suppliers. Additional non-destructive tests ensure quality.\nAs a company, we face the daily challenges of the market, both big and small, and our focus is always on our customers, our people and the business we do together. What makes us strong is what has made us strong since we were founded in 1852; the Ashcroft difference is the difference and strength of our people.\nPresident and CEOSteve Culmone\nCommitment in our actions, whether it concerns quality, adherence to deadlines or our interpersonal dealings, is what defines Ashcroft. We live our company's values every single day, with heart, brain and pragmatic action.\nVice President/General Manager (Europe &amp; Africa)Sven Richter\nAs a company, we face the daily challenges of the market, both big and small, and our